                    <span>This book is about  a boy named Merlin who is sent on a quest to heal the dark hills. While he is doing this, he finds his mother. But when they meet she is infected by the shadow of death. So now Merlin is off to learn the seven songs of wizardry. He must find the souls of each of the seven songs befor he can go into the Otherworld well. He has one month to learn the souls and get back to his mother befor she dies. I recommend this book to 7th through 9th grade.
<br />
<br />This book was great. The book i read was interseting if you like books about midievil times. The plot kpet me guessing the whole way through the book. After last year when I had to read a book thatmy teacher assigned to a group, I just loved it. That book was The Fires of Merlin. by T.A. Barron. I got hooked on the book set. There are Several books in this set. But I will tell you to read them in order because you will get confused. The frist book is THe Lost Years of Merlin. They are all great books.</span>
                  
              
